{"tid":1710250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水埗髮花湧現　淫風如昔日東莞","createTime":"2019-11-12T06:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T07:27:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f98b1274c1e93143f90df32864427fc7f4c53ab7","tid":1710250,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:21:27.000Z","msg":"復古色情髮廊近年湧現深水埗，成行成市的簡陋髮廊，標榜極廉價剪髮服務，甚至有按摩、足浴提供，惟店內總有2、3名衣着性感的「髮花」坐近大門，向途經的中老年男子大拋媚眼，甚至明目張膽兜搭生意，開價提供色情服務。區內婦女大感滋擾，警方接獲的相關投訴亦上升，惟掃黃次數卻減少，立法會議員直指警力減弱致賣淫活動猖獗，促加強打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191112/photo/bkn-20191112051047925-1112_00822_001_01p.jpg?20191112051314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191112%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191112051047925-1112_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20191112051314&h=a4a41426&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n深水埗近年湧現多間色情髮廊，有街坊坦言情況如90年代的東莞，店內髮花一般為內地口音，吸引不少上年紀男士尋歡作樂，惟區內良家婦女出入卻大感滋擾。其中，單是醫局街就有至少3間，設於舊樓地舖，店內坐着2至3名年約40多歲、打扮得花枝招展的大媽，不時向途經男士拋媚眼，甚至會開門拉客；部分就站在店外兜搭生意。「要唔要按摩？包舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」有坐在店外的髮花更直接提出「200蚊齋做」，暗示性服務。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191112/photo/bkn-20191112051047925-1112_00822_001_03p.jpg?20191112051314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191112%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191112051047925-1112_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20191112051314&h=7d9fd829&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n一街之隔的海壇街亦有至少2間同類髮廊，及一間類似格局的按摩店，店內一般有布簾暗格或暗房，甚至房內有樓梯直上舊樓。每間店內亦有2至3名髮花，她們大多以按摩作招徠，有人表明開價「全套服務」收500港元，可即時到舊樓單位交易。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191112/photo/bkn-20191112051047925-1112_00822_001_02p.jpg?20191112051314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191112%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191112051047925-1112_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20191112051314&h=fcbabd0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">醫局街一間髮型屋內，坐着3名年約40多歲、打扮得花枝招展的大媽，不時向途經男士拋媚眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，甚至會開門拉客。</span></div>"},{"pid":"7f670661896171bbe4df3935fbdd33e10fca6bba","tid":1710250,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:24:24.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n想問下你係咪有份五毛 分化撚的 資料？"},{"pid":"386dba4522f2dfb8c0d491a6512516e7c84e3367","tid":1710250,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7f670661896171bbe4df3935fbdd33e10fca6bba","tid":1710250,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:24:24.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n想問下你係咪有份五毛 分化撚的 資料？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:25:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EiHKwpz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEiHKwpz.gif&h=6ab0f373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/11/10/BxHVLe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F11%2F10%2FBxHVLe.png&h=2abf1a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">* 本名單已加入會員註冊日期以供參考</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2d2c61641f8a2754c0f27814f3159484d871929f","tid":1710250,"uid":198590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:28:32.000Z","msg":"我寫左個bot<br />\n打算係啲五毛開post時就覆佢<br />\n提醒其他網友<br />\n<br />\n但我而家仲收集緊資料<br />\n<br />\n請問你介唔介意我拎你啲資料去參考？"},{"pid":"247560a74e36c405477547ee20ffe327de81599a","tid":1710250,"uid":257293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d2c61641f8a2754c0f27814f3159484d871929f","tid":1710250,"uid":198590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:28:32.000Z","msg":"我寫左個bot<br />\n打算係啲五毛開post時就覆佢<br />\n提醒其他網友<br />\n<br />\n但我而家仲收集緊資料<br />\n<br />\n請問你介唔介意我拎你啲資料去參考？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"wow nice"},{"pid":"5180a7c1d4bd3072e0eaab93e4591e3a9e78d17e","tid":1710250,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"247560a74e36c405477547ee20ffe327de81599a","tid":1710250,"uid":257293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d2c61641f8a2754c0f27814f3159484d871929f","tid":1710250,"uid":198590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:28:32.000Z","msg":"我寫左個bot<br />\n打算係啲五毛開post時就覆佢<br />\n提醒其他網友<br />\n<br />\n但我而家仲收集緊資料<br />\n<br />\n請問你介唔介意我拎你啲資料去參考？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"wow nice"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"最近五毛/分化/mon post狗/網軍好嚴重<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bb0c06d2a79b6c98d78dedf7ae52d281becf0f6b","tid":1710250,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d2c61641f8a2754c0f27814f3159484d871929f","tid":1710250,"uid":198590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:28:32.000Z","msg":"我寫左個bot<br />\n打算係啲五毛開post時就覆佢<br />\n提醒其他網友<br />\n<br />\n但我而家仲收集緊資料<br />\n<br />\n請問你介唔介意我拎你啲資料去參考？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:53:12.000Z","msg":"我個 list 仲有好多值得完善嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n巴打唔介意嘅話可以拎其他手足整嘅 list 用住先<br />\n<br />\n【長期置頂】連登三毛清單 (持續更新)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652371</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"857e16f18adb9e7c1e65dd310abe3ce5b936ba9e","tid":1710250,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"附近荔枝角道及欽州街亦有類似髮廊，約400米範圍內就有逾10間。有地區人士更指色情髮廊數目在近年大幅上升，區內有逾40間，部分兼營按摩、足浴等，一般下午3時起出沒搵食，傍晚6時放工時間是高峰期。有髮花透露，地舖月租約1.5萬港元，一般2至3人夾租，每日生意約3至4單。<br />\n<br />\n執業大律師陸偉雄指，髮花於髮廊門口或街上兜搭提供色情服務，可被視為在公眾地方、或在公眾可見的情況下，為不道德目的而唆使其他人，有機會觸犯《刑事罪行條例》，最高可判罰款1萬港元及監禁6個月。<br />\n<br />\n陸續指，如髮廊內有多於1名妓女，髮廊老闆亦有機會被控「經營賣淫場所」，最高可判處10年監禁，若髮花與老闆攤分收入，更有可能被控「依靠他人賣淫的收入為生」。他提醒，即使業主不是色情髮廊老闆，但處所全部或部分用作賣淫場所，又有證據顯示業主知情或有份參與，則可能被控「出租處所以供用作賣淫場所」，最高可判監禁7年。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員郭家麒直言情況不能接受，亦會對街坊造成嚴重困擾。他指，問題源於政府無意認真解決問題，執法部門亦無有效打擊，認為只有加強執法情況才會有改善。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，今年1至10月深水埗警區接獲涉及區內色情活動的投訴有68宗，直逼去年全年的69宗；而首10個月並進行53次掃黃行動，有69人被捕，而去年全年就進行82次行動，有97人被捕。"},{"pid":"1e105e088b30a9bd41721d69578423714a85e2d7","tid":1710250,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:16:21.000Z","msg":"觀塘瑞和街康寧道，砵蘭街，上海街<br />\n<br />\n如果可以集結清左D北方妖怪就好"},{"pid":"125aa09792067084765fe3a5d5c8a000268376ce","tid":1710250,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"北方好唔掂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d86639b4a84efe7c74f1bf5cedb233308e88b22","tid":1710250,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"老雞都要500 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16fce53ff0439a0cec629f9b5cbea503f6e2c20","tid":1710250,"uid":43809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"隔住個moon 都聞到陣藥油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ed6ee2022553cb564d9a01425cd627b0c61229","tid":1710250,"uid":213631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d2c61641f8a2754c0f27814f3159484d871929f","tid":1710250,"uid":198590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:28:32.000Z","msg":"我寫左個bot<br />\n打算係啲五毛開post時就覆佢<br />\n提醒其他網友<br />\n<br />\n但我而家仲收集緊資料<br />\n<br />\n請問你介唔介意我拎你啲資料去參考？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c443fc8525949da086961527671243bda0836b","tid":1710250,"uid":313848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4mpOHwY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mpOHwY.gif&h=f5f52967&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ef02750373fbf0e998f9d164b13e051c7390c94","tid":1710250,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">40多歲</span></span></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪又係d藍絲廢老幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不推文回覆</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}